snippet.title: Parkitect launches on November 29th!
snippet.description:
The 1.0 release that adds the campaign mode to our theme park builder and management game Parkitect launches on November 29th!

Available on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/453090/Parkitect/
Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/parkitect
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/parkitect

Site: http://themeparkitect.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ParkitectGame
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ThemeParkitect/
